 编码规则如下：（简记为&lt;span class=&#34;black&#34;&gt;上&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;green&#34;&gt;下&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;blue&#34;&gt;右&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;red&#34;&gt;左&lt;/span&gt;）&lt;br /&gt;
